    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nFALL OUT BOY - CENTURIES\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTabbed by: ThatWogBoy  (Paul Scaramella)\r\nTuning: Standard EADG\r\n\r\nLots of breaks in the song, listen to it for timing...\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro/Chorus\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------| \r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10-10-10-10-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-------------------------------------------------------------|  X2\r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10\\-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]VERSE 1 \r\nG|--------|\r\nD|--------|\r\nA|--------| (49 SECOND MARK)\r\nE|--0--0--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-10-10-10-10-10-10-10-10-------------------------------------|\r\nE|-----------------------------------------8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8-5-5-5-5-10-10-10-10-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]PRE-CHORUS\r\nG|-------|\r\nD|-------|\r\nA|-------|\r\nE|--10\\--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]CHORUS\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------| \r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10-10-10-10-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-------------------------------------------------------------|  X2\r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10\\-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]VERSE 2\r\nG|--------|\r\nD|--------|\r\nA|--------| AT 1:50 AND 1:59\r\nE|--0--0--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]PRE-CHORUS\r\nG|-------|\r\nD|-------|\r\nA|-------|\r\nE|--10\\--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]CHORUS\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------| \r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10-10-10-10-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-------------------------------------------------------------|  X2\r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10\\-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]BRIDGE\r\nG|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7/10-10-10-10-10-10-10-10\\3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3\\0-0-0-0/5-5-5-5-|\r\nE|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------| \r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10-10-10-10-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-7-9-9-7-9-9-7-9-9-7-9-9-7-----|\r\nD|---------------------------9-7-| (TRIPLETS!)\r\nA|-------------------------------|\r\nE|-------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]OUTRO\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10-10-10-10-|[/tab]\r\n \r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------17(X8)-|  \r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0/3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3/8-8-8-8-8-8-8-8\\5-5-5-5/10--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| \\  slide down\r\n| h  hammer-on\r\n| p  pull-off\r\n| ~  vibrato\r\n| +  harmonic\r\n| x  Mute note\r\n\r\nThanks for rating :)\r\n\r\n===============================================================================",
